{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["夢幻の邂逅\n\n<size=45>願いを叶える「カミ」<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"無限の宇宙、無数の次元、数多の世界……それらを数限りなく観測してきて……","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":900012,"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"食指の動いた世界をピックアップしては、その世界の参考になりそうな事象を色々と試してきたものね","dir":1,"actorName":"テスター","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"鏡面海域を使えば、大概どうにかなっちゃうからねーこの間宇宙のどっかの星も観測できちゃったんじゃない？","dir":1,"actorName":"ピュリファイアー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"でも……今回ばかりは鏡面海域での実験がちょっとだけ裏目に出たわね","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"まさか利用したはずの世界に、逆用されてしまうだなんて……","dir":1,"actorName":"テスター","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"そこまで深刻でもないんじゃない？こんなの「ちょっかいをかけられた」程度でしょ？","dir":1,"actorName":"ピュリファイアー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"私たちの技術力に介入してくる存在とその力……それが問題なのよ","dir":1,"actorName":"テスター","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"何者か知る由もないけど……あの世界には中枢プログラムと同等……もしくはそれ以上の存在が控えているわ","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"？？？そいつのせいで投影した人形ちゃんたちが艤装をつけてパワーアップしたってこと？","dir":1,"actorName":"ピュリファイアー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"それだけじゃないわ……その存在は、あんなメッセージまで寄越してきたのよ？","dir":1,"actorName":"テスター","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"あの台詞……余程の自信がないと吐けないわよね","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"──おまえたちの「願い」はなんだ？","dir":1,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"願いを叶えてやる……でも、言外に「相応の代償を寄越せ」とも言ってきたわね","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"代償なく叶う願いなどありはしないけど……人間の記録からすれば、払う代償も叶う願いも、えげつないのがセオリーよね","dir":1,"actorName":"テスター","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"猿の手──だったかな？そういうのって基本ろくでもないよね","dir":1,"actorName":"ピュリファイアー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900021,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"その存在が私たちの願いを聞き入れたとして、叶えた暁にはどんな代償を望むことやら。でも残念だけど……","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"…………","dir":1,"actorName":"テスター","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900011,"blackBg":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"私たちは「プログラム」――最初から「願い」などないのよ。ふふふ…","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900012,"blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"LINKPREHEAT17","fadeOut":1.5}